description:
-- THIS IS A TWO PLAYER EXPERIENCE -- 

- Destroy all video ARTIFACTS;

Enjoy this VRC aesthetic experience with a friend!
<p>This is a multiplayer prototype build in Unity 2D + Photon2 following the Beginner's Guide to Multiplayer Game Development in Unity Course. The Pixel Art and UI are inspired by the VHS &amp; VCR aesthetics. </p>

- The TV atmosphere was created with Unity's Post-Processing Effects and Unity's ParticleSystem with a little help from EZCameraShake for extra feedback;
Controls:
<p>WASD To move - SPACE To dash</p>

- Work together to destroy all ARTIFACTS;

Code - Music &amp; Art Made by Thomas Guana - Not Your Typical Dev
